@startuml Error_Recovery_Sensor_Failure
skinparam sequenceMessageAlign center
skinparam responseMessageBelowArrow true
skinparam BoxPadding 10

title <size:16><b>Error Recovery - Sensor Failure Detection</b></size>\n<size:12><i>Graceful Degradation with Auto-Recovery</i></size>

participant "STM32" as STM32
participant "SHT3X\nSensor" as SHT3X
participant "ILI9225\nDisplay" as Display
participant "UART Link" as UART
participant "ESP32" as ESP32
participant "MQTT\nBroker" as MQTT
participant "Web\nInterface" as Web

note over STM32 #FFD700: Single/Periodic measurement requested

STM32 -> SHT3X: I2C Read measurement
activate SHT3X

alt I2C Timeout/NACK
    SHT3X --> STM32: HAL_TIMEOUT / HAL_ERROR
    STM32 -> STM32: Log: I2C communication failed
    STM32 -> STM32: Set temp=0.0, hum=0.0
    note right of STM32 #FF6B6B: Hardware communication error

else CRC Check Failed
    SHT3X -> STM32: Data received
    STM32 -> STM32: Validate CRC
    STM32 -> STM32: CRC mismatch detected
    STM32 -> STM32: Set temp=0.0, hum=0.0
    note right of STM32 #FF6B6B: Data corruption detected

else Sensor Disconnected
    SHT3X --> STM32: No response
    STM32 -> STM32: Set temp=0.0, hum=0.0
    note right of STM32 #FF6B6B: Sensor not responding
end
deactivate SHT3X

STM32 -> STM32: DataManager_Update (with 0.0 values)
STM32 -> Display: Show error indicator:\ntemp=0.0, hum=0.0
activate Display
Display -> Display: Display shows "Sensor Error"\nor red values
deactivate Display

alt MQTT Connected
    STM32 -> STM32: Format JSON with error values
    note right of STM32: {"mode":"SINGLE","timestamp":1729699200,\n"temperature":0.0,"humidity":0.0}

    STM32 -> UART: Transmit error JSON
    activate UART
    UART -> ESP32: Data received
    deactivate UART

    activate ESP32
    ESP32 -> ESP32: Parse JSON
    ESP32 -> ESP32: JSON_Parser_IsSensorFailed()\nreturns true
    ESP32 -> ESP32: Log: Sensor failure detected

    ESP32 -> MQTT: Publish error data
    activate MQTT
    MQTT -> Web: Forward
    deactivate MQTT

    Web -> Web: Display error state
    Web -> Web: Show alert:\n"Sensor communication error"
    deactivate ESP32

else MQTT Disconnected
    STM32 -> STM32: Buffer error data to SD
    note over STM32 #FF6B6B: Error records also buffered
end

note over STM32 #FFD700: System continues operation

STM32 -> STM32: Next measurement cycle
STM32 -> SHT3X: Retry I2C communication

alt Sensor Recovered
    activate SHT3X
    SHT3X -> STM32: Valid data
    deactivate SHT3X
    STM32 -> STM32: Parse valid temp & humidity
    STM32 -> Display: Clear error indicator
    STM32 -> STM32: Resume normal operation
    note over STM32, Web #87CEEB: <b>System automatically recovered</b>

else Sensor Still Failed
    STM32 -> STM32: Continue with 0.0 values
    note over STM32 #FFD700: Retry on each measurement
end

@enduml